document_data.Possessions:
She carried a ''[[ring of teleportation]]'', until [[Tespril]], her apprentice, filched it. At the time of her death, she wore a dark robe. She also wore an amulet that protected her against all poisons, almost certainly a ''[[periapt of proof against poison]]''.

She also bore a scrying element, a round sphere of crystal, through which she saw not just events but also thoughts to which she responded, strongly implying it was almost certainly a ''[[crystal ball]]''{{cite book/Crown of Fire/TPB 2002|63-64|3}} with ''[[detect thoughts]]''.{{cite book/Crown of Fire/TPB 2002|148|8}}

Gathlarue carried a number of enchanted rings that glowed blue when activated; those were destroyed soon after.{{cite book/Crown of Fire/TPB 2002|172-173|10}} She controlled [[gargoyle]]s{{cite book/Crown of Fire/TPB 2002|170|10}} through such rings.
